The paper discusses challenges and mitigation techniques for free space optical communication, which involves the use of optical carriers for communication links in space. This topic falls under the intersection of several computer science sub-disciplines, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), optics (cs.OH), systems and control (cs.SY), and performance analysis (cs.PF).
